            consists of letters between Pierce and his friends and literary colleagues. The
            clippings mainly refer to the publication of Pierce's works. Also included is a volume
            entitled "Cultural Change in Eastern North Carolina as Reflected in Some of the Novels
            of Inglis Fletcher and Ovid Pierce."</abstract>
